<L>__{interior kathleen's store day}
<A>__{kathleen is sitting on a stool reading to a group of children, including annabel and matt, who are crammed into her store. joe is watching, along with some parents as kathleen reads from a roald dahl book.}
<L>__{interior kathleen's store later}
<A>__{matt is sitting on the floor reading a book. kathleen is showing annabel a copy of a book called betsy tacy.}
<C>__{kathleen}
<D>__{this is her best friend tacy, whose real name is anastasia, and then in the next book betsy and tacy become friends with tib, whose real name, i am sorry to tell you, is thelma.}
